Description: Safe, quiet community in Northern Calvert County, about 30 minutes from AAFB, Annapolis, Washington DC and Northern VA. We are 5 blocks from the beach front of Chesapeake Bay! Apartments come with washer/dryer, dishwasher, balcony/patio, access to fitness center, picnic areas, car wash and public beach for free! Monthly rental rate includes water and sewer, trash, parking and all maintenance. We even supply your light bulbs! Make the time to come and see us... you won't regret it!
